    ('Concurrent Teacher Education .3 Intermediate/Senior (Grades 7-12)','These programs focus on grades seven to twelve, with an emphasis on secondary school.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','All majors - English (ENG4U), one 4U math.French Studies majors only - One of FSF4U, FEF4U or FIF4U.Dramatic Arts majors only - Attendance at DART Invitational mandatory.Visual Arts majors only - Submission of Visual Arts portfolio mandatory','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
    ('Computing and Network Communications','We.9ve teamed up with the School of Applied Computing and Engineering Sciences at Sheridan College to develop a program where you may complete your Brock degree and a three-year diploma in Telecommunications Technology from Sheridan College in just 4.5 years.','http://www.cosc.brocku.ca/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.70%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min. 70%)','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Concurrent Teacher Education .3 Primary/Junior (Grades K-6)','You.9ll study for six years to complete an Honours BA in Child and Youth Studies and a Bachelor of Education (BEd) at the same time.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','English (ENG4U).One 4U math (Mathematics of Data Management - MDM4U preferred).Students admitted directly from secondary school..For teaching at the Primary-Junior level (Grades K-6).','Faculty of Education'),
    ('Concurrent Teacher Education .3 Junior/Intermediate (Grades 4-10)','These programs focus on grades four to ten, with an emphasis on elementary school.','https://brocku.ca/education/programs/','English (ENG4U).One 4U math','Faculty of Applied Health Sciences'),
