    ('Earth Sciences','The Earth Sciences program trains geoscientists .4 scientists who study the Earth and other planets in order to better understand their origin and history.','https://brocku.ca/mathematics-science/earth-sciences/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U).Two from: Biology (SBI4U), Physics (SPH4U), Earth and Space Science (SES4U), Chemistry (SCH4U), or second 4U math','Faculty of Mathematics and Science'),
    ('Economics','Study the .cscience of choice.d .4 learning how limited resources can best be used to meet the needs of individuals and society. You.9ll look at how individual consumers choose to spend their time and money, and how producers predict and respond to consumer needs.','https://brocku.ca/social-sciences/economics/','English (ENG4U).Advanced Functions (MHF4U) (min.65%) or Calculus and Vectors (MCV4U) (min. 65%)','Faculty of Social Sciences'),
