    ('Dramatic Arts','As a Dramatic Arts (DART) student, you.9ll work with the very best faculty, artists and theatre professionals from Niagara, the GTA and beyond.','https://brocku.ca/miwsfpa/dramatic-arts/','English (ENG4U).Attendance at DART Invitational mandatory.','Faculty of Humanities'),
